    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四西凉兵",
        "张济",
        "樊稠",
        "韩遂",
        "马腾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四西凉兵、马腾、韩遂同上，二纛旗随上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马腾",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各整行装收兵将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩遂",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "衔枚息鼓避锋芒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马腾",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，前面已近大山口。急急趱行，恐有伏兵，截杀不便！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四西凉兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四大铠 （内同白） 杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "韩遂",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，你听喊杀之声渐近。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马腾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾已令庞德、马超断后。我与贤弟前行便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四军士、四大铠引张济、樊稠同上，会阵。四军士、四大铠、樊稠、四西凉兵、韩遂自两边分下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马腾哪里走！快快住马，与你比试三合！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马腾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "逆贼，你不思奋力王家，反助贼为虐；俺奉天讨逆，还不下马受缚！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派胡言，放马过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马腾、张济同起打。马腾下，张济追下。韩遂上，樊稠追上，打韩遂败下，樊稠追下。马腾上，张济追上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马超上，接战，马腾下。马超打张济败下，马超追下。樊稠追韩遂同上，庞德上，接战，韩遂下。庞德打"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "樊稠下，庞德追下。四军士、四大铠、四西凉兵同上，攢下。张济、樊稠追马腾、韩遂同上，打，四军士、"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四大铠同上，围战。四西凉兵、马超、庞德同上，救出马腾、韩遂，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济、樊稠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马腾、韩遂已败，穷寇莫追。就此回军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四军士、四大铠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今番对垒军威壮，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一战成功败西凉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊稠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得胜回军凯歌唱，"
        },
        {
          "character": "樊稠",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "英名大振保边疆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张济、樊稠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，收兵者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四军士、四大铠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖尾声〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
